  GrantedFeatures: []
  Description: Hours spent training with your preferred weapons, learning and developing
    new combat techniques, have made you particularly effective with your weapons
    of choice. Choose one weapon group. Your proficiency rank increases to master
    with the simple weapons, martial weapons, and unarmed attacks in that group,
    and to expert with the advanced weapons in that group. You gain access to the
    critical specialization effects of all weapons and unarmed attacks for which
    you have master proficiency.
